snippet.title: Space Hole 2020 in 2020
snippet.description:
In the year 2020, you still gotta go in the space hole!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1393310/Space_Hole_2020/

Space Hole 2020 is a video game and procedural visualizer. Adventure, and the Freeform Machine, awaits in Space Hole 2020's allegorical dive into the history of reality. Portrayed by a journey between different phases of universal development, simple controls, high system requirements, and a very serious photosensitivity warning: Space Hole 2020!


A video game and digital toy by Sam Atlas.
Indirect successor to Space Hole 2018 & 2016. Each game represents or is set in the year, there is no overlapping narrative.
